Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Fail loudly on labels.csv/config class mismatch

- config.LABELS_CSV: Challenge 2020's two class sets write separate label
  files inside one shared WORK_DIR, so switching C2020_CLASS_SET cannot
  silently invalidate an existing CSV. Images stay shared.
- labels_io.read_labels(): single validated reader used by zero_shot_eval,
  extract_features, finetune_clip and train_biomedcoop. Reports DATASET,
  C2020_CLASS_SET, CLASSES, the file's own columns and the fix command,
  before the image-encoding pass instead of after it.
