 headers by dataset
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

ECGImageDataset._path built its candidate tuple eagerly, so int('A0147')
raised before the loop could test 'A0147.png' — which exists. Candidates
are now built lazily and a genuinely missing image raises FileNotFoundError
naming the record and directory instead of failing later inside PIL.

Report headers said 'PTB-XL test fold' regardless of the active dataset;
they now use labels_io.dataset_label().
---
